WEBVTT

01:31.010 --> 01:34.920
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.229 --> 01:36.950
I didn't lose!

01:35.850 --> 01:39.300
[1998]

01:37.150 --> 01:38.590
Lele cheated.

01:38.710 --> 01:40.479
I didn't lose!

01:40.759 --> 01:41.350
Alright.

01:41.350 --> 01:42.350
It's just a game of soccer.

01:42.350 --> 01:43.120
Winning won't make you taller,

01:43.120 --> 01:44.789
and losing won't make you shrink, alright?

01:44.789 --> 01:45.840
Come on. Wash your hands and let's eat.

01:45.840 --> 01:46.310
Stop crying.

01:46.310 --> 01:47.840
I really didn't lose!

01:47.840 --> 01:48.310
Alright.

01:48.310 --> 01:49.310
I didn't lose.

01:49.310 --> 01:50.370
Alright, alright.

01:50.400 --> 01:52.920
Getting carried away with
that fake crying, huh?

01:52.920 --> 01:54.400
A real man should be able to
win with grace

01:54.400 --> 01:55.660
and lose with dignity.

01:55.710 --> 01:56.240
Besides,

01:56.280 --> 01:57.410
this isn't over yet.

01:57.680 --> 01:58.509
If you're not convinced,

01:58.509 --> 01:59.640
just win it back next time.

01:59.640 --> 02:00.170
Exactly.

02:00.200 --> 02:01.070
Everyone, come eat!

02:01.070 --> 02:02.270
Come on, let's go eat.

02:02.760 --> 02:03.790
That's life—

02:04.230 --> 02:05.230
until the very end,

02:05.230 --> 02:05.920
no one knows

02:05.920 --> 02:07.180
who the real winner is.

02:08.360 --> 02:09.120
He's just a kid.

02:09.120 --> 02:10.720
Why are you telling him this?

02:10.750 --> 02:11.210
Come on.

02:13.030 --> 02:13.630
Let's eat.

02:16.860 --> 02:20.200
[Episode 31]
[The Real Winner]

02:21.240 --> 02:22.630
The one who will receive 5% of

02:22.630 --> 02:24.090
Chengrong Group's shares

02:24.590 --> 02:25.079
is...

02:27.840 --> 02:28.590
Zhao...

02:33.240 --> 02:33.680
Hui.

02:37.240 --> 02:38.470
I knew I'd win!

02:40.120 --> 02:41.050
Come on! Come on!

02:41.520 --> 02:42.470
Go, Zhaohui!

02:45.630 --> 02:46.150
Come on!

02:46.800 --> 02:47.860
Come on! Well done!

02:48.360 --> 02:50.150
Go, Zhaohui! Go!

02:51.030 --> 02:51.560
Thanks.

02:51.750 --> 02:53.880
Congratulations. Congratulations.

02:56.610 --> 02:58.740
Thanks, everyone. Let's have a drink!

03:03.630 --> 03:04.150
Zhaoji,

03:04.800 --> 03:06.460
are you really okay with this?

03:07.030 --> 03:08.430
Daddy just favors Zhaohui more.

03:08.430 --> 03:09.890
What's not to be okay with?

03:09.910 --> 03:11.040
Congrats, Zhaohui.

03:11.840 --> 03:13.640
I don't get your brotherly love.

03:19.590 --> 03:19.910
Here.

03:19.700 --> 03:22.670
[Du Family Banquet]

03:27.910 --> 03:28.520
Remember,

03:28.590 --> 03:30.520
don't hurt that guy surnamed Zhou.

03:38.680 --> 03:40.410
-Quick, get in the car!
-Get in.

03:44.430 --> 03:44.960
Let's go.

04:02.710 --> 04:03.440
Stop the car!

04:17.510 --> 04:18.240
Stop the car!

04:22.950 --> 04:23.680
Stop the car!

04:26.800 --> 04:27.530
Stop the car!

04:32.150 --> 04:33.390
You dare hit me?

04:41.920 --> 04:42.560
Why wouldn't Old Man

04:42.560 --> 04:44.000
let us touch that guy surnamed Zhou?

04:44.000 --> 04:44.600
How would I know

04:44.600 --> 04:45.720
what Old Man is thinking?

04:45.720 --> 04:48.180
He just thinks so highly of
that Xia Xiaolan.

04:48.190 --> 04:48.720
But

04:49.190 --> 04:50.790
they took that Xiao guy away.

04:51.310 --> 04:52.909
Quan, you must be upset, too.

05:05.480 --> 05:06.070
Mr. Xiao.

05:06.800 --> 05:07.930
Do you still have it?

05:08.190 --> 05:08.600
Yes.

05:11.390 --> 05:12.750
I can't do anything right.

05:12.750 --> 05:14.150
They all say I'm an idiot.

05:15.000 --> 05:16.270
I bet they never thought I'd be the one

05:16.270 --> 05:17.400
to steal the ledger.

05:27.430 --> 05:28.090
Zhou Cheng.

05:29.360 --> 05:30.090
What is this?

05:32.110 --> 05:34.170
Liu Tianquan's smuggling accounts.

05:47.390 --> 05:47.920
Xiaolan.

05:48.480 --> 05:49.240
Are you okay?

05:49.600 --> 05:50.130
I'm fine.

05:50.720 --> 05:51.580
Okay, let's go.

05:51.720 --> 05:52.360
Ms. Xia.

05:53.830 --> 05:55.240
Chairman Du would like to
have a word with you.

05:55.240 --> 05:56.240
This way, please.

06:11.190 --> 06:11.920
Don't worry.

06:12.240 --> 06:13.920
San has left safely.

06:14.120 --> 06:15.070
It shows Chairman Du

06:15.070 --> 06:16.730
really didn't plan to harm us.

06:18.800 --> 06:20.330
I'll wait for you here then.

06:26.120 --> 06:27.650
Ms. Xia, please have a seat.

06:31.070 --> 06:32.240
Ms. Xia,

06:33.390 --> 06:35.190
are you satisfied with our hospitality

06:35.190 --> 06:35.870
today?

06:37.070 --> 06:38.550
You are too kind, Chairman Du.

06:38.550 --> 06:40.950
The banquet you prepared is
excellent, of course.

06:40.950 --> 06:42.070
It's just a pity

06:42.120 --> 06:43.190
that most guests

06:43.240 --> 06:44.640
didn't come for the food.

06:45.830 --> 06:47.070
Then are you satisfied with

06:47.070 --> 06:48.800
the outcome of the competition

06:49.680 --> 06:50.810
between my two sons?

06:52.390 --> 06:53.480
Whoever wins or loses

06:53.480 --> 06:55.280
is Chengrong Group's business.

06:55.600 --> 06:57.190
I'm Du Zhaohui's consultant.

06:57.190 --> 06:58.800
I'm certainly happy he won.

06:59.720 --> 07:00.560
But surely,

07:01.240 --> 07:02.360
Chairman Du, you wouldn't have

07:02.360 --> 07:03.830
declared Du Zhaohui the winner

07:03.830 --> 07:05.230
just to please me, right?

07:07.430 --> 07:08.160
Chairman Du,

07:08.360 --> 07:10.800
since you asked me here,
shouldn't we talk about

07:10.800 --> 07:12.310
the smuggling leads you mentioned

07:12.310 --> 07:13.600
in the invitation?

07:14.120 --> 07:15.120
Ms. Xia,

07:15.120 --> 07:16.980
you really are straightforward.

07:17.040 --> 07:19.300
Then I won't beat around the bush either.

07:19.750 --> 07:20.880
I've made up my mind—

07:21.270 --> 07:22.750
I'll shut down all of Chengrong Group's

07:22.750 --> 07:24.600
smuggling activities.

07:25.070 --> 07:27.070
If I find anyone

07:27.070 --> 07:29.000
still involved in smuggling,

07:29.040 --> 07:30.830
I'll hand them over

07:31.070 --> 07:33.270
to the Shengcheng Police immediately.

07:33.680 --> 07:34.360
That way,

07:35.070 --> 07:37.360
Mayor Tang should be pleased, right?

07:38.260 --> 07:39.890
I think your decision

07:39.920 --> 07:41.120
is absolutely right.

07:41.680 --> 07:42.510
But I must

07:42.510 --> 07:43.510
remind you—

07:43.920 --> 07:45.590
this is only the minimum requirement

07:45.590 --> 07:46.830
for Chengrong Group to do business
in Shengcheng,

07:46.830 --> 07:48.430
not a gesture of goodwill.

07:48.920 --> 07:50.070
What Shengcheng needs

07:50.070 --> 07:51.390
isn't any particular group

07:51.390 --> 07:52.159
or capital,

07:52.800 --> 07:54.190
but a law-abiding enterprise

07:54.190 --> 07:55.390
that can

07:55.750 --> 07:57.720
contribute to economic growth.

08:01.330 --> 08:02.090
Ms. Xia,

08:02.120 --> 08:03.510
you really are a woman of principle.

08:03.510 --> 08:04.680
No wonder Zhaohui

08:05.120 --> 08:06.630
didn't catch your eye.

08:07.800 --> 08:09.400
You flatter me, Chairman Du.

08:09.430 --> 08:10.510
Du Zhaohui is

08:10.510 --> 08:12.170
a very good business partner,

08:12.560 --> 08:13.720
but feelings

08:13.950 --> 08:15.750
and business are two entirely
different matters,

08:15.750 --> 08:16.480
aren't they?

08:17.070 --> 08:17.800
Otherwise,

08:18.160 --> 08:19.040
Chairman Du,

08:19.240 --> 08:21.100
if you really wanted to please me,

08:21.240 --> 08:22.630
wouldn't it be simpler

08:22.920 --> 08:24.580
to hand over the other person?

08:30.310 --> 08:31.120
Ms. Xia.

08:33.260 --> 08:34.440
Actually, by coming to Kong Island,

08:34.440 --> 08:35.789
you and Mr. Zhou have already gotten

08:35.789 --> 08:37.200
what you wanted.

08:38.440 --> 08:39.720
And I haven't laid a finger

08:39.720 --> 08:41.150
on Mr. Zhou.

08:43.200 --> 08:45.330
One shouldn't be too greedy, you know?

08:48.750 --> 08:49.670
In that case,

08:50.270 --> 08:52.530
I understand what you mean, Chairman Du.

08:52.720 --> 08:54.780
I hope you'll also keep your promise.

08:55.200 --> 08:56.530
I'll take my leave then.

08:56.550 --> 08:58.150
Do you really not want to know

08:58.170 --> 08:59.720
why I chose Zhaohui

08:59.720 --> 09:01.120
instead of Zhaoji?

09:02.720 --> 09:03.480
Du Zhaoji

09:03.510 --> 09:05.670
is too much like you
when you first made your fortune—

09:05.670 --> 09:06.360
ambitious

09:06.550 --> 09:07.680
and without limits.

09:07.790 --> 09:08.550
And you know

09:08.870 --> 09:10.080
that kind of approach doesn't work anymore

09:10.080 --> 09:11.150
in this day and age.

09:11.960 --> 09:13.690
Kong Island is returning soon.

09:15.790 --> 09:17.150
Impressive.

09:17.840 --> 09:18.360
You know,

09:18.360 --> 09:19.290
sometimes I feel

09:20.550 --> 09:21.440
you're nothing like

09:21.440 --> 09:22.750
a twenty-year-old.

09:23.200 --> 09:24.200
Thanks for the compliment.

09:24.200 --> 09:25.530
I'll take my leave then.

09:41.600 --> 09:42.960
That Xia Xiaolan

09:43.150 --> 09:44.240
is so rude.

09:44.360 --> 09:46.160
Just because she's the mayor's daughter,

09:46.160 --> 09:48.820
she thinks she can talk to you like that,
Master?

09:50.870 --> 09:51.790
I don't think

09:52.030 --> 09:53.510
you need to be so sarcastic

09:53.510 --> 09:55.080
over a little grudge

09:55.080 --> 09:56.960
with your cousin.

09:59.380 --> 09:59.900
I...

10:00.360 --> 10:01.150
Look,

10:01.790 --> 10:03.390
since you already have a new identity,

10:03.390 --> 10:05.120
just play your role properly.

10:08.110 --> 10:08.750
Master.

10:09.750 --> 10:10.810
You knew all along?

10:16.150 --> 10:16.750
It's fine.

10:17.870 --> 10:18.630
You know,

10:19.030 --> 10:21.600
anyone who gets close to me—

10:22.030 --> 10:24.160
I make sure to know them inside and out.

10:25.120 --> 10:26.870
Actually, I don't care

10:26.870 --> 10:28.200
about your background.

10:29.790 --> 10:31.150
What matters is

10:31.720 --> 10:33.030
that you serve me well.

10:34.080 --> 10:35.630
Whether you are Xia Ziyu

10:35.960 --> 10:37.000
or Vivi

10:37.200 --> 10:39.030
doesn't matter.

10:40.160 --> 10:41.470
What matters is

10:43.870 --> 10:44.730
that you are now

10:45.390 --> 10:47.240
the mother of my child.

10:50.390 --> 10:51.870
This is an indisputable fact.

10:51.870 --> 10:53.670
No one would dare to question it.

10:56.840 --> 10:58.550
Then can I go anywhere?

11:00.080 --> 11:01.550
Can I go to Shengcheng?

11:03.000 --> 11:03.960
Of course.

11:13.210 --> 11:14.670
According to Du Chengrong,

11:14.670 --> 11:16.530
he gave up that ledger on purpose.

11:17.510 --> 11:18.750
I've checked the ledger.

11:18.750 --> 11:20.240
The signature belongs to Liu Tianquan.

11:20.240 --> 11:21.150
It won't be long

11:21.150 --> 11:23.000
before Liu Tianquan is arrested.

11:23.000 --> 11:24.510
Giving up just Liu Tianquan

11:24.510 --> 11:26.320
to secure Shengcheng's resources—

11:26.320 --> 11:28.240
Du Chengrong is being far too optimistic.

11:28.240 --> 11:29.910
I don't believe he'd really give up

11:29.910 --> 11:31.480
all that off-the-books income.

11:31.480 --> 11:32.270
In the short term,

11:32.270 --> 11:33.750
Du Zhaohui will be Chengrong Group's

11:33.750 --> 11:35.550
representative in Shengcheng.

11:36.120 --> 11:36.790
If Du Zhaohui

11:36.790 --> 11:38.450
can stick to the current path,

11:38.790 --> 11:39.630
then at least Chengrong

11:39.630 --> 11:41.490
won't be left behind by the times.

11:43.840 --> 11:44.640
Young Master.

11:44.790 --> 11:45.480
Aren't you going back

11:45.480 --> 11:46.880
to Shengcheng with them?

11:48.560 --> 11:49.550
Our cooperation was only for the purpose

11:49.550 --> 11:51.150
of winning this competition.

11:51.150 --> 11:52.360
Now that the competition is won,

11:52.360 --> 11:53.760
the cooperation is over.

11:54.510 --> 11:55.630
What reason do I have

11:55.630 --> 11:56.790
to stay by her side?

11:58.330 --> 11:59.330
As for Du Zhaoji,

11:59.360 --> 12:01.290
he won't accept defeat willingly.

12:01.480 --> 12:04.210
I have to stay in Kong Island
to guard against him.

12:09.360 --> 12:10.360
When you go back,

12:11.240 --> 12:12.840
settle her consulting fees.

12:12.960 --> 12:13.320
Okay.

12:13.870 --> 12:15.000
Now that she's gone,

12:15.620 --> 12:17.420
who knows when we'll meet again.

12:20.170 --> 12:21.320
Young Master, you... You...

12:21.320 --> 12:23.080
Are you lovesick again?

12:41.360 --> 12:42.480
You old fool...

12:42.870 --> 12:43.840
You old fool!

12:48.660 --> 12:49.750
All my efforts to be a dutiful son

12:49.750 --> 12:50.750
were for nothing!

12:51.480 --> 12:52.960
In the end, you still gave

12:54.200 --> 12:55.670
to Du Zhaohui.

12:57.600 --> 13:00.930
You've really become more and more
muddle-headed with age.

13:21.790 --> 13:24.320
I'll take back everything
that belongs to me.

14:01.200 --> 14:02.330
Go report to Ms. Xia—

14:02.670 --> 14:04.480
the Golden Sands Pool
model room is finished.

14:04.480 --> 14:04.910
Got it.

14:08.710 --> 14:11.110
[Kong Island]

14:11.580 --> 14:15.540
[Chengrong Group]

14:25.560 --> 14:26.090
Hua,

14:26.390 --> 14:27.240
make an appointment with Dr. Liu

14:27.240 --> 14:28.240
for a heart check-up.

14:28.240 --> 14:29.440
Where... Where does your heart hurt?

14:29.440 --> 14:30.510
I'll go get the doctor right away.

14:30.510 --> 14:32.370
Every time I think of Xia Xiaolan,

14:32.600 --> 14:33.600
my heart aches.

14:33.780 --> 14:39.440
♪ Love has faded,
and so has the bond between us ♪

14:34.510 --> 14:35.270
Since the birthday banquet,

14:35.270 --> 14:36.910
I haven't seen her for 2 months.

14:36.910 --> 14:38.110
Two months, you know?

14:39.150 --> 14:40.360
I'm afraid I've got lovesickness.

14:39.760 --> 14:48.650
♪ Yet, why do I still love you? ♪

14:40.510 --> 14:41.790
Lovesickness?

14:42.080 --> 14:43.480
You need to see a psychiatrist
for lovesickness,

14:43.480 --> 14:44.280
Young Master.

14:46.840 --> 14:48.080
You know,

14:48.790 --> 14:49.850
I see them often...

14:50.750 --> 14:52.120
Our premium buildings
even come with a household registration,

14:52.120 --> 14:53.390
so there's no reason for them to be cheap.

14:53.390 --> 14:54.870
The first floor can be priced a bit higher

14:54.870 --> 14:56.520
since it comes with
an underground parking space.

14:56.520 --> 14:57.960
The second and third floors
are good levels—

14:57.960 --> 14:59.030
easy to walk up to

14:59.030 --> 15:00.200
and not damp to live in.

15:00.200 --> 15:01.550
The fourth and fifth floors
have great views,

15:01.550 --> 15:03.910
so their prices definitely
shouldn't be lowered.

15:03.910 --> 15:05.390
And the top floor comes with a garden,

15:05.390 --> 15:07.000
so pricing it a bit higher is no problem.

15:07.000 --> 15:07.330
Okay.

15:07.670 --> 15:08.470
Ms. Xia, look—

15:08.670 --> 15:10.530
the newly installed scale model.

15:10.630 --> 15:11.550
See if there's anything

15:11.550 --> 15:12.880
that needs adjustment.

15:19.480 --> 15:20.080
Gong Yang.

15:21.080 --> 15:22.540
You made this scale model?

15:24.360 --> 15:25.480
So is there anything

15:25.480 --> 15:27.140
that needs correcting to you?

15:27.270 --> 15:28.480
I don't think there is.

15:28.480 --> 15:29.610
I'll check it again.

15:30.200 --> 15:30.630
Okay.

15:35.800 --> 15:37.260
Send the drawings in a bit.

15:37.510 --> 15:38.390
This Building 9—

15:38.390 --> 15:39.790
let's make it the special offer building.

15:39.790 --> 15:40.120
Okay.

15:40.150 --> 15:41.840
The lighting probably isn't very good.

15:41.840 --> 15:42.770
Let's sell it for

15:43.240 --> 15:44.200
2,000 yuan per square meter.

15:44.200 --> 15:44.910
2,000...

15:45.030 --> 15:46.960
2,000 yuan per square meter
is the special offer?

15:46.960 --> 15:47.470
Yes.

15:47.830 --> 15:49.240
Compared to the list price,

15:49.240 --> 15:50.770
it's already much cheaper.

15:51.360 --> 15:52.270
Write this down.

15:52.270 --> 15:53.600
This is the viewing process

15:53.600 --> 15:54.660
for the launch day:

15:54.720 --> 15:56.650
first, we show the customers
the scale model.

15:56.650 --> 15:57.890
Once they've decided on a unit type,

15:57.890 --> 15:58.940
they pay a 1,000-yuan

15:58.940 --> 15:59.840
reservation deposit,

15:59.840 --> 16:00.630
and then we can take them

16:00.630 --> 16:01.870
into the residential complex.

16:01.870 --> 16:02.330
Ms. Xia.

16:02.480 --> 16:05.270
You mean they have to pay before viewing,

16:05.270 --> 16:05.750
right?

16:06.480 --> 16:06.840
Yes.

16:07.150 --> 16:08.080
That 1,000 yuan

16:08.130 --> 16:09.200
will be counted towards the house price.

16:09.200 --> 16:10.240
We won't just take it.

16:10.240 --> 16:11.080
If they aren't willing

16:11.080 --> 16:12.240
to pay even this 1,000 yuan,

16:12.240 --> 16:13.360
how can we expect them to fork out

16:13.360 --> 16:14.150
more money?

16:15.200 --> 16:17.130
This is called precise screening.

16:17.150 --> 16:18.010
Serious buyers

16:18.080 --> 16:19.680
will save us a lot of trouble.

16:20.240 --> 16:21.370
Brilliant, Ms. Xia.

16:21.630 --> 16:23.550
If there are no questions,

16:23.550 --> 16:24.840
compile the information

16:24.840 --> 16:25.650
I just gave you,

16:25.650 --> 16:27.000
and send it to the newspaper
for publication.

16:27.000 --> 16:27.330
Okay.

16:27.390 --> 16:28.870
There are 2 months until the launch.

16:28.870 --> 16:29.950
We can't stop advertising.

16:29.950 --> 16:30.790
The closer we get,

16:30.790 --> 16:31.720
the more effort we need to put in.

16:31.720 --> 16:32.050
Okay.

16:34.320 --> 16:34.840
Ms. Xia,

16:35.150 --> 16:36.360
the model room is ready.

16:36.360 --> 16:37.390
Shall we go over now?

16:37.390 --> 16:37.750
Okay.

16:39.790 --> 16:40.390
Gong Yang.

16:42.150 --> 16:43.750
The scale model is well made.

16:43.840 --> 16:45.030
There are still many tasks
for you to handle

16:45.030 --> 16:46.090
before the launch.

16:46.120 --> 16:47.180
Keep up the effort.

16:47.320 --> 16:47.790
Ms. Xia,

16:48.360 --> 16:49.240
I'll do my best.

16:51.750 --> 16:53.610
No one understands better than me

16:53.670 --> 16:54.870
how precious

16:54.870 --> 16:55.930
a second chance is.

16:57.000 --> 16:57.960
If I can give someone

16:57.960 --> 16:58.720
this chance,

16:59.120 --> 17:00.240
I don't want to be stingy.

17:00.240 --> 17:00.770
Let's go.

17:01.000 --> 17:01.360
Okay.

17:07.030 --> 17:07.750
Paying 50,000 yuan a year

17:07.750 --> 17:09.550
for a regular membership

17:09.790 --> 17:11.750
versus 100,000 yuan for a VIP membership

17:11.750 --> 17:12.589
for golf—

17:12.589 --> 17:14.390
what exactly is the difference?

17:14.520 --> 17:16.170
Regular members and us VIPs

17:16.200 --> 17:17.530
are not in the same zone.

17:17.579 --> 17:19.000
There's also premium membership,

17:19.000 --> 17:20.069
which is by invitation only.

17:20.069 --> 17:21.640
It's not something you can just buy.

17:21.640 --> 17:22.720
It's that hard?

17:23.859 --> 17:25.560
I think Auntie is right.

17:25.720 --> 17:26.829
Instead of spending time here,

17:26.829 --> 17:27.589
we'd be better off working in the shop.

17:27.589 --> 17:29.510
We could close several big deals
in one morning.

17:29.510 --> 17:30.440
Exactly.

17:31.030 --> 17:32.150
Zhenzhu, Auntie.

17:32.270 --> 17:32.790
Coming here

17:32.790 --> 17:34.540
isn't about playing golf.

17:34.680 --> 17:35.590
It's for the

17:35.590 --> 17:37.650
exclusive social environment here.

17:37.830 --> 17:38.880
People prefer to associate

17:38.880 --> 17:40.240
with those on their own level.

17:40.240 --> 17:42.240
It's called exchanging resources.

17:43.160 --> 17:43.830
Mr. Chen.

17:45.360 --> 17:46.370
Hello, hello.

17:46.400 --> 17:46.750
Look.

17:46.790 --> 17:48.070
I don't have your contact info yet.

17:48.070 --> 17:48.330
So...

17:48.330 --> 17:49.390
I have it, I have it.

17:49.680 --> 17:50.110
Here.

17:52.070 --> 17:53.350
Chen Xiliang from Luna.

17:53.350 --> 17:53.960
Here's my card.

17:53.960 --> 17:54.490
Alright.

17:54.680 --> 17:55.280
Thank you.

17:55.310 --> 17:56.240
Let's keep in touch.

17:56.240 --> 17:56.830
Sure.

17:56.830 --> 17:57.760
Nice to meet you.

17:59.200 --> 18:01.440
Doing business is that simple?

18:02.000 --> 18:03.880
Starting from scratch is hard, of course.

18:03.880 --> 18:05.550
But once you have a solid foundation,

18:05.550 --> 18:07.350
stepping onto the right platform

18:07.350 --> 18:09.240
just opens up all kinds of opportunities.

18:09.240 --> 18:11.400
Then we should have asked your mom
to come along today.

18:11.400 --> 18:12.590
She's now Luna's

18:12.920 --> 18:14.200
regional manager.

18:14.550 --> 18:16.280
She needs a platform like this.

18:16.400 --> 18:16.920
But my mom

18:16.920 --> 18:18.200
is not only a regional manager now—

18:18.200 --> 18:19.700
she's also the mayor's wife.

18:19.700 --> 18:20.550
This kind of environment

18:20.550 --> 18:21.550
doesn't suit her.

18:21.810 --> 18:22.200
I forgot.

18:22.200 --> 18:23.680
O-Our Teresa is the same.

18:23.790 --> 18:25.510
She can't come unless she's paid.

18:25.510 --> 18:26.240
Right, right.

18:26.240 --> 18:27.240
-She's a superstar, after all.
-Chen.

18:27.240 --> 18:28.220
You're talking nonsense.

18:28.220 --> 18:29.950
That's completely different.

18:29.960 --> 18:30.790
And once we do,

18:30.790 --> 18:33.030
we're gonna have parks for children,

18:33.030 --> 18:34.690
entertainment areas, and...

18:34.750 --> 18:36.510
Isn't that Ms. Xia?

18:37.110 --> 18:38.240
What a coincidence.

18:40.440 --> 18:40.970
Zhaohui!

18:42.830 --> 18:43.360
Xiaolan!

18:44.440 --> 18:47.420
[Shengcheng: A City of Innovation
and Charm—Welcome!]

19:11.880 --> 19:13.610
Mr. Du is honored to be invited,

19:13.750 --> 19:15.210
but he's abroad right now.

19:15.960 --> 19:17.090
So I'll be attending

19:17.350 --> 19:18.200
on his behalf.

19:20.700 --> 19:21.880
Ladies and gentlemen,

19:21.880 --> 19:22.810
hello everyone.

19:23.070 --> 19:24.720
We gather here today

19:25.100 --> 19:26.960
to witness the opening of
the Oriental Green

19:26.960 --> 19:28.510
Golf Club.

19:28.690 --> 19:30.320
I hope this green course

19:30.350 --> 19:31.830
can bring joy to everyone.

19:31.850 --> 19:34.180
She dares to come to Shengcheng so openly—

19:34.350 --> 19:35.480
it seems Chairman Du

19:35.550 --> 19:38.150
has already taken care of
her identity issues.

19:38.880 --> 19:40.400
Why did Old Man send her?

19:40.830 --> 19:42.750
It makes sense that Chairman Du
doesn't show up,

19:42.750 --> 19:43.900
but shouldn't he have

19:43.900 --> 19:44.960
let you, Young Master Du,

19:44.960 --> 19:46.160
attend on his behalf?

19:46.790 --> 19:48.250
Why let her do the tee-off?

19:49.310 --> 19:49.960
Xia Ziyu

19:50.030 --> 19:51.890
is pregnant with Old Man's child.

19:52.110 --> 19:53.590
She took the chance to tell him

19:53.590 --> 19:55.920
that she wants to learn
how to do business.

19:56.320 --> 19:57.440
For such public appearances,

19:57.440 --> 19:59.030
she's always the first to volunteer.

19:59.030 --> 20:01.110
Then I must congratulate you,
Young Master Du,

20:01.110 --> 20:03.240
on getting another brother or sister.

20:03.350 --> 20:04.510
Don't tease me.

20:05.390 --> 20:06.790
Old Man lets her have the spotlight

20:06.790 --> 20:08.120
just to keep me in check—

20:08.200 --> 20:09.040
to let me know

20:09.310 --> 20:10.400
that even though I won the shares,

20:10.400 --> 20:11.730
I shouldn't be too smug.

20:12.390 --> 20:13.310
He won't really give his fortune

20:13.310 --> 20:14.350
to her.

20:15.030 --> 20:15.640
But you—

20:15.790 --> 20:17.000
her hatred for you is real.

20:17.000 --> 20:18.400
You'd better be careful.

20:20.550 --> 20:21.790
Xia Ziyu?

20:22.200 --> 20:23.480
You mean that Xia Ziyu?

20:24.720 --> 20:25.680
Where is she?

20:26.640 --> 20:27.300
Over there.

20:29.790 --> 20:31.160
Isn't she a fugitive?

20:31.480 --> 20:32.940
We should call the police.

20:33.200 --> 20:34.480
She's got a new identity.

20:34.480 --> 20:35.250
Even if we report her to the police,

20:35.250 --> 20:36.680
they won't be able to catch her
anytime soon.

20:36.680 --> 20:37.550
Dear friends...

20:37.550 --> 20:38.030
My goodness.

20:38.030 --> 20:39.720
Why does she look like that?

20:40.070 --> 20:40.590
Ready?

20:41.200 --> 20:41.640
Three.

20:42.960 --> 20:43.550
Two.

20:44.480 --> 20:44.960
One.

20:45.510 --> 20:46.240
Tee off!

20:49.720 --> 20:51.960
-Great!
-Nice!

20:53.640 --> 20:55.360
Thank you all, distinguished guests.

20:55.360 --> 20:56.480
Now, Oriental Green

20:56.480 --> 20:57.400
Golf Club

20:57.420 --> 20:58.900
is officially open!

21:01.440 --> 21:02.600
So that's Xia Ziyu?

21:02.920 --> 21:03.480
Yeah.

21:03.960 --> 21:06.160
The notorious Xia Ziyu.

21:07.400 --> 21:08.440
Shall we go out for a drink?

21:08.440 --> 21:08.970
Zhaohui!

21:10.750 --> 21:11.480
If I'd known you wanted to come,

21:11.480 --> 21:13.010
you could have come with me.

21:13.030 --> 21:15.290
Why are you stuck in the regular section?

21:15.880 --> 21:17.160
Do you guys

21:17.160 --> 21:17.920
smell that?

21:18.350 --> 21:19.920
That musky, foul stench—

21:20.440 --> 21:21.400
you know, like a wild fox

21:21.400 --> 21:21.920
that's been caged for ages

21:21.920 --> 21:23.110
just got released.

21:23.550 --> 21:24.550
Unbearably foul.

21:24.680 --> 21:25.200
Xiaolan,

21:25.200 --> 21:25.700
let's go.

21:25.700 --> 21:26.160
Let's get some fresh air.

21:26.160 --> 21:27.890
Why leave as soon as I come over?

21:28.240 --> 21:30.640
Don't think of yourself as insignificant.

21:31.510 --> 21:33.400
Come to think of it, isn't all this wealth

21:33.400 --> 21:34.680
I have thanks to you?

21:36.200 --> 21:38.330
The person I should be most grateful to

21:38.880 --> 21:39.650
is you.

21:45.960 --> 21:48.270
Seems like you two
have business to settle.

21:48.270 --> 21:49.670
I'll excuse myself then.

21:52.270 --> 21:52.830
Goodbye,

21:53.720 --> 21:54.450
Xia Xiaolan.

22:02.910 --> 22:03.920
Disgusting.

22:04.640 --> 22:05.300
Du Zhaohui.

22:07.070 --> 22:07.830
Is there something

22:07.830 --> 22:08.890
you want to tell me?

22:22.070 --> 22:23.870
I kept asking you out for coffee,

22:24.070 --> 22:25.400
but you never accepted.

22:25.960 --> 22:26.510
Now look—

22:27.440 --> 22:29.240
we're finally having coffee together.

22:29.240 --> 22:29.790
But this is probably

22:29.790 --> 22:30.990
the last cup, I guess.

22:32.400 --> 22:33.110
You know,

22:33.510 --> 22:34.270
back then,

22:34.480 --> 22:35.880
we weren't partners yet.

22:36.840 --> 22:38.110
I wanted to use a honey trap

22:38.110 --> 22:38.960
on Old Man.

22:39.750 --> 22:41.070
I noticed that Xia Ziyu

22:41.400 --> 22:42.510
was quite thick-skinned,

22:42.510 --> 22:43.610
and she was a fugitive.

22:43.610 --> 22:44.770
She was like a pawn delivered to my door.

22:44.770 --> 22:46.230
I'd be a fool not to use her.

22:48.350 --> 22:50.150
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

22:50.160 --> 22:50.920
I just couldn't find

22:50.920 --> 22:52.380
the right time to tell you.

22:53.510 --> 22:53.920
When I found out

22:53.920 --> 22:55.380
about your relationship,

22:56.200 --> 22:57.660
I thought this connection

22:58.160 --> 22:58.640
might be useful

22:58.640 --> 22:59.720
in the future,

23:00.400 --> 23:01.800
so I didn't say anything.

23:02.380 --> 23:03.040
But later,

23:03.070 --> 23:05.270
we started working together, you know.

23:05.590 --> 23:06.590
I was worried that

23:06.790 --> 23:07.920
once you found out,

23:08.310 --> 23:10.350
we wouldn't be able to
continue our partnership,

23:10.350 --> 23:11.960
so I didn't dare to say anything.

23:11.960 --> 23:14.640
There are actually things
you don't dare to do, Young Master Du?

23:14.640 --> 23:15.900
Harboring a fugitive,

23:16.230 --> 23:17.480
getting her plastic surgery,

23:17.480 --> 23:18.740
teaching her to dance,

23:18.830 --> 23:19.680
and even sending her

23:19.680 --> 23:21.140
to your own father's side—

23:21.750 --> 23:22.680
Young Master Du,

23:22.830 --> 23:24.760
I think you've got plenty of nerve.

23:26.640 --> 23:27.590
Let me guess.

23:28.550 --> 23:30.480
Don't tell me you also wanted to see

23:30.490 --> 23:31.480
if Xia Ziyu has the ability

23:31.480 --> 23:33.140
to seduce both father and son?

23:33.200 --> 23:34.110
If even Du Zhaoji

23:34.110 --> 23:35.200
takes her bait,

23:35.560 --> 23:37.800
then you could just sit back and watch

23:37.830 --> 23:39.830
the father and son
turn against each other, right?

23:39.830 --> 23:41.480
Don't... Don't put it like that.

23:41.480 --> 23:41.830
I...

23:43.240 --> 23:44.240
At the time, I couldn't figure out

23:44.240 --> 23:45.840
what my old man was thinking,

23:46.440 --> 23:47.350
and I wasn't willing to let

23:47.350 --> 23:49.810
the Du family be snatched away
by that loser.

23:51.960 --> 23:52.820
I've never been

23:53.030 --> 23:54.560
afraid of anyone in my life,

23:55.240 --> 23:56.440
but honestly...

23:57.880 --> 23:58.400
I really feared

23:58.400 --> 23:59.110
you'd never speak to me again

23:59.110 --> 24:00.040
because of this.

24:02.070 --> 24:03.030
I knew that

24:05.030 --> 24:06.480
we could never date.

24:07.160 --> 24:08.000
But if we could

24:08.030 --> 24:09.630
continue working together,

24:09.720 --> 24:10.980
that would be nice too.

24:12.510 --> 24:13.400
But it seems

24:14.400 --> 24:16.000
that's also impossible now.

24:17.880 --> 24:19.080
I have no one to blame.

24:19.830 --> 24:20.790
I can only blame myself

24:20.790 --> 24:22.190
for meeting you too late.

24:26.400 --> 24:27.030
Mr. Du.

24:28.550 --> 24:31.080
If there are suitable projects
in the future,

24:31.480 --> 24:33.940
it's not impossible for us
to work together.

24:36.920 --> 24:38.070
Actually, I've known for a long time

24:38.070 --> 24:39.200
that Xia Ziyu was sent by you

24:39.200 --> 24:40.460
to Chairman Du's side.

24:40.750 --> 24:41.960
Whether you admitted it or not

24:41.960 --> 24:43.490
wouldn't change anything.

24:43.630 --> 24:44.640
Anyway, this bad move

24:44.640 --> 24:46.040
has already been played.

24:47.030 --> 24:47.750
So,

24:47.920 --> 24:50.250
you were just waiting for me
to come clean?

24:50.920 --> 24:52.250
How could I be so stupid?

24:54.030 --> 24:54.760
Don't worry.

24:55.180 --> 24:56.160
Since I had the means

24:56.160 --> 24:57.550
to send her to Old Man,

24:58.030 --> 24:59.920
I have the means
to make her disappear immediately.

24:59.920 --> 25:00.590
Forget it.

25:01.160 --> 25:02.270
You've only just gotten your life

25:02.270 --> 25:03.800
on track in Shengcheng.

25:04.000 --> 25:05.440
Breaking the law for her

25:06.200 --> 25:07.200
won't be worth it.

25:08.730 --> 25:14.530
♪ Love has become a burden,
and being in love feels like a torment ♪

25:14.950 --> 25:20.390
♪ My heart is now filled with
bitter tears ♪

25:17.750 --> 25:19.590
She told me not to break the law.

25:20.980 --> 25:27.220
♪ Old feelings were intoxicating,
now I fear chasing them again ♪

25:21.680 --> 25:22.880
So she cares about me?

25:26.510 --> 25:27.240
Definitely.

25:27.840 --> 25:32.240
♪ Yet my infatuated heart
still longs to see you ♪

25:28.790 --> 25:30.520
She definitely cares about me.

25:33.160 --> 25:33.690
How much?

25:35.240 --> 25:36.240
Six. Six yuan.

25:36.590 --> 25:36.880
Alright.

25:36.880 --> 25:37.680
Here's 6 yuan.

25:37.690 --> 25:38.240
Come again.

25:38.240 --> 25:38.640
Okay.

25:44.960 --> 25:45.510
Junbao,

25:46.400 --> 25:47.350
what are you looking at?

25:47.350 --> 25:48.160
Get to work.

25:48.510 --> 25:49.110
Coming up.

25:49.130 --> 25:49.880
It's busy hour.

25:49.880 --> 25:51.010
Eat while it's warm.

25:54.440 --> 25:54.880
Drive.

25:55.750 --> 25:56.480
To Elegance.

26:05.780 --> 26:09.440
[Grand Opening of Golden Sands Pool]

26:21.790 --> 26:23.650
Why am I hearing that sound again?

26:40.150 --> 26:41.240
My dear Ms. Xia.

26:41.510 --> 26:43.400
You handle everything personally.

26:43.400 --> 26:44.240
Imagine how much pressure

26:44.240 --> 26:45.570
that puts on your staff.

26:53.680 --> 26:54.340
Zhou Cheng.

26:55.640 --> 26:56.720
I don't know why,

26:57.010 --> 26:58.450
but I've been having

26:58.480 --> 26:59.680
a bad feeling lately.

27:00.400 --> 27:01.070
In my mind,

27:01.070 --> 27:02.310
I keep seeing sudden images

27:02.310 --> 27:03.240
of a fire.

27:04.350 --> 27:05.000
It might be a glimpse of

27:05.000 --> 27:06.310
a future I've seen,

27:07.550 --> 27:09.640
but because my memories are all mixed up,

27:09.640 --> 27:11.500
I can't really recall it clearly.

27:11.960 --> 27:13.890
It makes me feel extremely uneasy.

27:15.510 --> 27:16.160
A fire?

27:19.310 --> 27:21.000
Since we can't confirm

27:21.000 --> 27:22.000
what the event is,

27:22.590 --> 27:23.680
let's take precautions

27:23.680 --> 27:24.440
in advance.

27:25.070 --> 27:25.800
For example,

27:26.310 --> 27:27.270
regarding the decor,

27:27.270 --> 27:28.560
reduce flammables,

27:28.590 --> 27:29.720
and ban open flames.

27:31.200 --> 27:31.590
Okay.

27:33.790 --> 27:35.120
Then help me check again

27:35.270 --> 27:36.000
if there's anything else

27:36.000 --> 27:37.460
that needs to be adjusted.

27:46.830 --> 27:49.310
Make sure all the decorations
are properly hung.

27:49.310 --> 27:50.640
And make sure everything looks neat

27:50.640 --> 27:51.570
and harmonious.

27:52.070 --> 27:52.530
Ge Jian.

27:52.990 --> 27:54.360
These are too flammable.

27:54.360 --> 27:54.960
Better forget it.

27:54.960 --> 27:56.090
Just take them down.

27:56.590 --> 27:57.390
Okay, Ms. Xia.

27:57.400 --> 27:57.920
Well,

27:58.200 --> 27:59.240
stop what you're doing.

27:59.240 --> 28:00.070
We're not hanging them up anymore.

28:00.070 --> 28:00.790
Take them down. Take them down.

28:00.790 --> 28:01.520
Okay. Got it.

28:01.750 --> 28:02.130
Come on,

28:02.130 --> 28:02.440
take them down.

28:02.440 --> 28:04.500
Thank you for your hard work.
Come on.

28:06.270 --> 28:06.920
Relax.

28:07.160 --> 28:08.360
Don't worry too much.

28:09.240 --> 28:09.640
Go sit.

28:09.660 --> 28:10.590
I'll get you a glass of water.

28:10.590 --> 28:11.000
Okay.

28:24.510 --> 28:25.590
An explosion occurred on the opening day

28:25.590 --> 28:27.600
of a property development in Shengcheng.

28:27.600 --> 28:29.240
Firefighters rushed to the scene
immediately

28:29.240 --> 28:31.040
to carry out rescue operations.

28:33.030 --> 28:33.440
Here.

28:34.310 --> 28:34.840
Xiaolan.

28:43.030 --> 28:43.830
What's wrong?

28:44.480 --> 28:45.140
Explosion.

28:46.160 --> 28:47.220
It's an explosion.

28:47.680 --> 28:48.720
I remember when I was young,

28:48.720 --> 28:50.160
I saw it on the TV news.

28:50.590 --> 28:52.480
In the 90s, there was a development

28:52.480 --> 28:54.340
that exploded on its opening day.

28:54.670 --> 28:56.400
Many homebuyers were injured.

28:56.550 --> 28:57.160
And later, that development

28:57.160 --> 28:57.880
was never sold—

28:57.880 --> 29:01.010
it became an abandoned,
unfinished building in the end.

29:02.450 --> 29:04.110
Since we already know about it

29:04.240 --> 29:06.060
and have taken protective measures,

29:06.060 --> 29:06.960
let's not worry excessively

29:06.960 --> 29:07.750
about things

29:07.770 --> 29:09.270
that haven't happened yet.

29:09.270 --> 29:09.880
Besides,

29:10.270 --> 29:11.530
the news in your memory

29:11.680 --> 29:13.740
might not be about Golden Sands Pool.

29:13.830 --> 29:15.090
Don't scare yourself.

29:15.350 --> 29:15.830
In a bit,

29:16.220 --> 29:17.830
I'll have all these hydrogen balloons

29:17.830 --> 29:18.750
taken down.

29:19.750 --> 29:20.200
Okay?

29:22.750 --> 29:23.200
Okay.

29:24.440 --> 29:25.170
Don't worry.

29:28.460 --> 29:31.840
[Grand Opening of Golden Sands Pool]

29:46.680 --> 29:47.480
Get me a drink.

29:48.880 --> 29:50.280
Why are you in such a rush?

29:53.890 --> 29:55.750
You used to be a boss in Longcheng,

29:56.000 --> 29:57.270
and now you live like a rat

29:57.270 --> 29:58.510
in this tiny dump

29:58.510 --> 29:59.880
of Shengcheng.

30:02.640 --> 30:04.640
What is it? Speak!

30:04.920 --> 30:05.510
Yixiong.

30:06.160 --> 30:08.560
Golden Sands Pool opens for sale tomorrow.

30:15.790 --> 30:18.200
Every piece of trash has its use.

30:18.880 --> 30:20.280
Make sure tomorrow's job

30:20.310 --> 30:21.240
gets done right.

30:21.920 --> 30:22.720
Do you hear me?

30:25.550 --> 30:26.200
Yixiong.

30:27.200 --> 30:28.030
That rich woman

30:28.030 --> 30:29.090
who came to see you—

30:29.480 --> 30:30.790
will she keep her word?

30:31.830 --> 30:32.400
What?

30:33.060 --> 30:34.590
You spent a few days behind the bars,

30:34.590 --> 30:35.890
and you've lost your nerve?

30:35.890 --> 30:37.240
Too scared to act without help now?

30:37.240 --> 30:38.070
Of course not.

30:38.790 --> 30:40.450
Even without that rich woman,

30:41.030 --> 30:42.640
we'll still avenge Liu.

30:43.000 --> 30:43.800
That's right.

30:44.240 --> 30:44.890
Absolutely. We must.

30:44.890 --> 30:45.570
We must.

30:53.880 --> 30:54.590
Yaozong.

30:55.410 --> 30:57.000
Let's drink to our heart's content today.

30:57.000 --> 30:57.460
Cheers.

30:57.460 --> 30:58.050
So happy.

30:58.790 --> 30:59.790
Have another sip.

31:01.710 --> 31:02.440
That's the spirit.

31:02.440 --> 31:03.070
Yaozong.

31:05.440 --> 31:06.700
I can't drink anymore.

31:10.550 --> 31:11.080
Yaozong?

31:16.030 --> 31:17.720
When you do your rounds tonight,

31:17.720 --> 31:19.310
make sure to check carefully.

31:19.310 --> 31:19.790
Okay.

31:20.000 --> 31:21.250
Check every building.

31:21.250 --> 31:22.510
Make sure there are no hazards.

31:22.510 --> 31:22.920
Okay.

31:30.470 --> 31:31.200
Who's there?

31:31.590 --> 31:32.650
What are you doing?

31:32.960 --> 31:33.830
He's stealing rebars!

31:33.830 --> 31:34.240
Get him!

31:34.240 --> 31:35.030
You guys, get him!

31:35.030 --> 31:35.490
Get him!

31:35.500 --> 31:36.290
Cut him off here!

31:36.290 --> 31:36.890
Catch him!

31:37.200 --> 31:37.860
Cut him off!

31:38.960 --> 31:39.960
Stop right there!

31:56.550 --> 31:57.030
Call the police.

31:57.030 --> 31:58.070
Call an ambulance! Quick!

31:58.070 --> 31:59.000
Yes, Manager Ge.

32:01.510 --> 32:02.240
Luo Yaozong?

32:03.160 --> 32:03.890
Luo Yaozong!

32:24.960 --> 32:25.360
Hello?

32:26.070 --> 32:26.530
Ms. Xia.

32:26.830 --> 32:29.750
Luo Yaozong fell from a building
at the construction site.

32:29.750 --> 32:31.320
Ge Jian, call the police immediately

32:31.320 --> 32:32.110
and secure the scene.

32:32.110 --> 32:33.110
Don't touch anything.

32:33.110 --> 32:34.240
I'll be right there.

32:39.920 --> 32:40.980
Hello? Zhou Cheng.

32:41.030 --> 32:43.560
Something bad happened
at Golden Sands Pool.

32:51.030 --> 32:51.490
Ms. Xia.

32:52.270 --> 32:53.350
How is Luo Yaozong?

32:53.510 --> 32:54.280
He's lucky to be alive.

32:54.280 --> 32:55.280
The place he fell

32:55.310 --> 32:56.680
happened to be where Mr. Wu

32:56.680 --> 32:57.720
had sand piled up.

32:57.930 --> 32:58.680
Was he in cahoots

32:58.680 --> 32:59.740
with the rebar thief?

32:59.740 --> 33:00.550
We don't know yet.

33:00.550 --> 33:01.760
We'll have to wait for
the police to investigate.

33:01.760 --> 33:02.680
Mr. Zhou and Mr. Liu

33:02.680 --> 33:04.310
are waiting for the police
at Golden Sands Pool.

33:04.310 --> 33:06.310
They asked me to bring Luo Yaozong
to the hospital first.

33:06.310 --> 33:06.790
Okay.

33:08.160 --> 33:08.590
San.

33:09.070 --> 33:10.830
I'll leave things here to you and Zhenzhu.

33:10.830 --> 33:12.270
Leave it to us. Don't worry.

33:12.270 --> 33:12.750
Ge Jian,

33:13.000 --> 33:14.000
come back with me.

33:14.270 --> 33:14.930
The trouble

33:15.400 --> 33:16.350
has just begun.

33:17.110 --> 33:17.710
We're off.

33:17.830 --> 33:18.960
Stay safe, you guys.

33:21.830 --> 33:24.030
Here's the security guard duty roster.

33:24.590 --> 33:26.110
The person involved has been taken
to the hospital.

33:26.110 --> 33:27.200
As for the details,

33:27.480 --> 33:28.740
we're not sure either.

33:35.240 --> 33:36.100
This is Ms. Xia.

33:37.920 --> 33:38.480
Xiaolan.

33:41.590 --> 33:42.520
Hello, Officer.

33:42.830 --> 33:43.960
I'm the person in charge of
Golden Sands Pool,

33:43.960 --> 33:44.690
Xia Xiaolan.

33:45.240 --> 33:45.740
Luo Yaozong

33:45.740 --> 33:46.800
is indeed one of our security guards.

33:46.800 --> 33:47.590
But tonight,

33:47.590 --> 33:49.160
we didn't schedule him for a shift.

33:49.160 --> 33:49.880
And Golden Sands Pool

33:49.880 --> 33:51.140
goes on sale tomorrow.

33:51.270 --> 33:53.160
Please make sure to investigate this
thoroughly as soon as possible.

33:53.160 --> 33:54.030
If things get out of hand,

33:54.030 --> 33:55.890
it will be very difficult for us
to manage.

33:55.890 --> 33:56.830
As for Luo Yaozong's situation,

33:56.830 --> 33:58.270
Mr. Zhou has told me about it.

33:58.270 --> 33:59.960
I've also checked the duty roster.

33:59.960 --> 34:00.830
And the others

34:00.850 --> 34:01.880
who were with Luo Yaozong

34:01.880 --> 34:03.590
have been taken to the police station.

34:03.590 --> 34:05.390
This case is indeed suspicious.

34:05.790 --> 34:07.200
We will get to the bottom of it.

34:07.200 --> 34:07.550
Okay.

34:08.190 --> 34:08.989
Officer Wang.

34:09.630 --> 34:10.480
Go with Mr. Liu

34:10.480 --> 34:11.440
to the crime scene again

34:11.440 --> 34:12.550
and see if there are any other clues.

34:12.550 --> 34:12.960
Yes, Sir.

34:12.960 --> 34:13.690
Come with me.

34:15.760 --> 34:16.219
Ms. Xia.

34:16.320 --> 34:17.710
Did you come from the hospital?

34:17.710 --> 34:18.110
Yes.

34:18.440 --> 34:19.840
How is Luo Yaozong doing?

34:20.510 --> 34:22.310
He's still being resuscitated.

34:22.550 --> 34:25.320
A life for a life! A life for a life!

34:25.320 --> 34:26.150
My grandson!

34:26.150 --> 34:34.440
A life for a life! A life for a life!

34:34.460 --> 34:35.980
Give me back my son!

34:36.440 --> 34:38.070
Yaozong was killed by them!

34:38.110 --> 34:39.159
A life for a life!

34:39.190 --> 34:40.550
Pay with your life, do you hear us?

34:40.550 --> 34:42.150
You shameless bitch!

34:42.719 --> 34:43.639
I'll kill you!

34:43.670 --> 34:45.550
A life for a life!

34:45.550 --> 34:46.190
What are you trying to do?

34:46.190 --> 34:46.920
Officers...

34:47.070 --> 34:48.870
They're so powerful and influential.

34:48.870 --> 34:50.000
Did you all see that?

34:50.570 --> 34:51.600
Even the police

34:51.630 --> 34:52.830
are siding with them!

34:53.110 --> 34:53.510
Right!

34:53.630 --> 34:55.630
Capitalists are harming the people!

34:55.630 --> 34:57.110
Even the police are in their pocket!

34:57.110 --> 34:57.440
Yeah!

34:57.670 --> 34:59.110
Let's rush them!

34:59.360 --> 35:00.230
Those two

35:00.230 --> 35:01.250
who were inciting the Luo family just now—

35:01.250 --> 35:02.390
follow them quietly.

35:02.390 --> 35:02.800
Right?

35:02.880 --> 35:04.230
They killed Yaozong!

35:04.510 --> 35:05.190
We have to see him,

35:05.190 --> 35:05.960
alive

35:06.150 --> 35:06.840
or dead!

35:07.070 --> 35:07.590
That's right!

35:07.590 --> 35:08.480
A life for a life!

35:08.480 --> 35:09.440
Stop, stop!

35:10.110 --> 35:10.670
Wait, wait!

35:10.670 --> 35:12.070
Stop making a scene here!

35:12.710 --> 35:14.150
Once we get to the bottom of it,

35:14.150 --> 35:15.410
we won't favor anyone.

35:15.550 --> 35:16.610
Make way, make way!

35:16.800 --> 35:17.930
Excuse me! Make way!

35:19.030 --> 35:20.290
Put down your weapons!

35:21.710 --> 35:22.360
Officers.

35:22.840 --> 35:24.580
We're from the Subdistrict Office.

35:24.580 --> 35:25.310
Luo Degui.

35:25.760 --> 35:27.030
What do you think you're doing?

35:27.030 --> 35:28.760
Do you want to lose your job
as Village Director or what?

35:28.760 --> 35:30.190
My son is dead.

35:30.710 --> 35:32.570
Whoever wants the job can take it.

35:32.760 --> 35:34.370
I don't give a damn!

35:34.400 --> 35:34.670
Yeah!

35:34.670 --> 35:36.000
Give me back my son!

35:36.610 --> 35:37.280
Calm down, everyone!

35:37.280 --> 35:38.710
Officer, let me say something.

35:38.710 --> 35:39.320
Calm down!

35:39.720 --> 35:40.810
Do you want to know

35:40.840 --> 35:42.240
how Luo Yaozong's doing?

35:42.480 --> 35:44.110
If you do, then shut up!

35:45.880 --> 35:47.210
Luo Yaozong isn't dead.

35:47.960 --> 35:48.960
He's still alive.

35:52.510 --> 35:53.940
If you don't want to see him

35:53.940 --> 35:55.320
and just want to cause trouble,

35:55.320 --> 35:56.720
then keep making a scene.

35:58.320 --> 35:59.050
She's lying!

35:59.550 --> 36:01.150
Luo Yaozong is already dead.

36:01.360 --> 36:03.110
Falling from such a high building—

36:03.110 --> 36:04.230
how could he possibly survive?

36:04.230 --> 36:04.630
Right!

36:04.840 --> 36:06.480
How did Yaozong fall?

36:06.510 --> 36:06.880
Exactly!

36:06.880 --> 36:08.280
Did you have someone push him?

36:08.280 --> 36:09.320
Did you push him?

36:09.440 --> 36:10.280
Fell?

36:11.900 --> 36:13.220
How do you know he fell?

36:15.030 --> 36:15.920
I never said

36:15.920 --> 36:17.590
Luo Yaozong fell.

36:17.760 --> 36:18.400
I... I...

36:19.920 --> 36:21.530
I... I heard it from them!

36:21.960 --> 36:22.760
Right, Baldy?

36:22.870 --> 36:23.600
They said it!

36:23.710 --> 36:24.510
Y-Yeah, right!

36:24.510 --> 36:25.550
I... I also heard

36:25.920 --> 36:26.930
i-it from others.

36:26.960 --> 36:28.670
Who exactly did you hear it from?

36:28.670 --> 36:30.030
There must be a source, right?

36:30.030 --> 36:30.510
Yeah.

36:32.960 --> 36:34.620
Fellow villagers of Ganquan.

36:35.920 --> 36:37.280
Luo Yaozong is not dead.

36:37.920 --> 36:40.030
He's undergoing emergency treatment
at the hospital at this moment.

36:40.030 --> 36:41.030
Regarding this matter,

36:41.030 --> 36:42.590
we will investigate thoroughly

36:42.590 --> 36:44.190
and give everyone an answer.

36:44.440 --> 36:45.150
However,

36:45.960 --> 36:47.440
until the truth is out,

36:47.920 --> 36:48.480
if anyone

36:48.670 --> 36:49.920
incites the crowd

36:49.920 --> 36:51.000
to riot again,

36:51.590 --> 36:52.790
we will make arrests.

36:53.000 --> 36:53.660
My grandson

36:54.030 --> 36:55.030
really isn't dead?

36:55.030 --> 36:55.960
H-He's really not dead?

36:55.960 --> 36:56.620
He's alive.

36:57.320 --> 36:58.070
Chief Luo.

36:58.440 --> 37:01.190
Luo Yaozong is being resuscitated
in the hospital right now.

37:01.190 --> 37:03.190
Which is more important—
your grandson's life

37:03.190 --> 37:04.250
or causing a scene?

37:05.550 --> 37:06.190
Someone

37:06.510 --> 37:07.880
must be behind this.

37:09.040 --> 37:09.840
Get the villagers

37:09.840 --> 37:10.770
to go home first.

37:11.320 --> 37:12.150
I promise

37:12.400 --> 37:14.060
I'll get to the bottom of this.

37:16.190 --> 37:17.550
If my grandson dies,

37:19.440 --> 37:20.770
I'll have the villagers

37:21.510 --> 37:23.110
tear down your shabby house.

37:23.880 --> 37:25.030
Then I'll find a rope

37:25.670 --> 37:27.270
and hang myself at this door!

37:27.280 --> 37:28.030
Let's see

37:28.630 --> 37:30.150
who you can sell to then!

37:30.570 --> 37:31.880
Dad, calm down. Calm down.

37:31.880 --> 37:34.540
As long as Yaozong is okay.
That's what matters.

37:35.880 --> 37:36.510
Folks!

37:36.800 --> 37:39.030
Thank you for standing up for Yaozong.

37:39.550 --> 37:40.860
Officials from the Subdistrict Office

37:40.860 --> 37:41.390
are here,

37:41.510 --> 37:42.760
and so are the police.

37:43.320 --> 37:44.580
Please go back for now.

37:44.630 --> 37:46.440
We'll deal with everything
once Yaozong's out of danger.

37:46.440 --> 37:46.920
Go back.

37:47.230 --> 37:48.960
Let's go, folks. Let's go home.

37:52.550 --> 37:52.960
Stop!

37:53.150 --> 37:53.810
Don't move.

37:53.960 --> 37:54.510
What are you doing?

37:54.510 --> 37:55.480
You two can't leave.

37:55.480 --> 37:55.760
Hey,

37:55.840 --> 37:56.670
we are villagers.

37:56.670 --> 37:57.320
Why can't we leave?

37:57.320 --> 37:58.610
Yeah, why can't we go?

37:58.880 --> 37:59.740
Get back there!

38:00.000 --> 38:00.480
Don't move, you hear me?

38:00.480 --> 38:01.760
I think you two know quite a lot.

38:01.760 --> 38:02.920
Why don't you explain it to the officers?

38:02.920 --> 38:03.670
No, this...

38:03.710 --> 38:04.320
You two,

38:04.920 --> 38:06.070
come in and have a chat with us.

38:06.070 --> 38:06.710
Take them away.

38:06.710 --> 38:08.170
It's none of our business!

38:08.950 --> 38:10.480
What are you doing? What's this about?

38:10.480 --> 38:12.210
They have nothing to do with us!

38:13.230 --> 38:14.160
Leave this to us.

38:14.190 --> 38:14.590
Okay.

38:14.800 --> 38:15.690
Thank you then.

38:15.920 --> 38:17.250
-Let's go.
-Let's go in.

38:19.400 --> 38:21.000
Yaozong!

38:21.510 --> 38:22.510
Yaozong!

38:22.590 --> 38:23.510
Yaozong!

38:23.880 --> 38:24.670
Yaozong!

38:25.480 --> 38:26.480
Yaozong!

38:26.840 --> 38:27.590
Yaozong!

38:27.590 --> 38:28.190
Calm down. Calm down.

38:28.190 --> 38:29.240
What are you trying to do?

38:29.240 --> 38:30.450
My son is in surgery.

38:30.480 --> 38:31.400
Why won't you let us in?

38:31.400 --> 38:31.920
Quiet!

38:32.110 --> 38:33.550
My grandson is in there!

38:33.710 --> 38:34.770
This is a hospital.

38:34.960 --> 38:36.160
Family members stay.

38:36.190 --> 38:37.850
Everyone else, please leave.

38:38.920 --> 38:39.550
Okay. Okay.

38:39.550 --> 38:40.080
Officer,

38:40.150 --> 38:41.150
we'll cooperate.

38:41.630 --> 38:42.510
You guys go first.

38:42.510 --> 38:43.570
Go back, everyone.

38:44.920 --> 38:45.450
Officer.

38:45.710 --> 38:46.970
I'm Yaozong's father.

38:47.000 --> 38:48.190
This is Yaozong's grandfather.

38:48.190 --> 38:49.320
We're both his family.

38:49.320 --> 38:50.360
Can we go in now?

38:50.840 --> 38:52.590
Your son is in surgery in there.

38:52.840 --> 38:53.960
Just wait a moment for now.

38:53.960 --> 38:54.760
Wait a moment.

38:56.280 --> 38:57.230
Sit down first.

38:58.880 --> 39:00.670
I just got off the phone with the station.

39:00.670 --> 39:01.870
We've confirmed that

39:02.150 --> 39:03.140
those who were stealing the steel

39:03.140 --> 39:04.220
with Luo Yaozong

39:04.510 --> 39:06.170
aren't from Ganquan Village.

39:06.440 --> 39:07.970
They weren't close before.

39:08.510 --> 39:10.410
But recently,
they started drinking together

39:10.410 --> 39:11.760
and got close all of a sudden.

39:11.760 --> 39:13.560
Clearly, someone planned this.

39:14.320 --> 39:15.590
We've looked into Luo Yaozong.

39:15.590 --> 39:16.320
He

39:16.320 --> 39:17.800
usually throws his weight around,

39:17.800 --> 39:18.550
but he doesn't really have

39:18.550 --> 39:20.000
any major grudges with anyone.

39:20.000 --> 39:20.960
So we suspect...

39:21.190 --> 39:22.550
Someone's trying to use him

39:22.550 --> 39:23.710
to cause a fatal accident,

39:23.710 --> 39:25.370
targeting Golden Sands Pool.

39:26.360 --> 39:26.820
Ms. Xia,

39:27.360 --> 39:29.510
have you had any conflicts

39:29.760 --> 39:31.480
or made any enemies recently?

39:32.470 --> 39:34.400
No specific conflicts or grudges.

39:35.500 --> 39:36.250
But I do have

39:36.280 --> 39:37.340
2 suspects in mind.

39:37.800 --> 39:38.840
Only those two

39:39.080 --> 39:39.840
are capable of

39:39.840 --> 39:41.570
such disregard for human life.

39:42.710 --> 39:43.880
One is Ke Yixiong,

39:44.510 --> 39:45.910
and the other is Xia Ziyu.

39:47.190 --> 39:48.360
We know Ke Yixiong.

39:48.800 --> 39:49.320
He used to be

39:49.320 --> 39:50.710
a gang leader

39:50.920 --> 39:52.070
near Longcheng Railway Station.

39:52.070 --> 39:53.230
Now that he's in Shengcheng,

39:53.230 --> 39:54.560
he's still up to no good.

39:54.710 --> 39:56.030
But he's very cautious.

39:56.030 --> 39:56.670
When he acts,

39:56.670 --> 39:57.840
he uses his lackeys,

39:58.550 --> 39:59.690
keeping himself well-hidden.

39:59.690 --> 40:01.490
We've been keeping an eye on him.

40:01.630 --> 40:03.560
A while back, his underling Cao Liu

40:03.840 --> 40:04.840
hired thugs to attack a friend of mine

40:04.840 --> 40:05.840
and got locked up.

40:06.360 --> 40:06.880
There are a few other

40:06.880 --> 40:08.070
lackeys of his

40:08.360 --> 40:09.150
who were detained for a few days

40:09.150 --> 40:10.210
and then released.

40:10.400 --> 40:11.190
Those are probably the only men

40:11.190 --> 40:12.230
he has left.

40:14.840 --> 40:16.240
What about the other one,

40:16.280 --> 40:16.810
Xia Ziyu?

40:16.920 --> 40:17.520
Who is she?

40:19.070 --> 40:20.360
Xia Ziyu is a fugitive.

40:21.110 --> 40:22.970
She once hired someone to hurt me.

40:23.000 --> 40:24.730
Later, she fled to Kong Island.

40:24.880 --> 40:25.590
Officer,

40:26.030 --> 40:28.510
I suspect the two of them
are conspiring together.

40:28.510 --> 40:30.170
Can we keep this quiet for now?

40:30.440 --> 40:31.880
We'll open for sales as planned tomorrow.

40:31.880 --> 40:33.480
If they have another move planned,

40:33.480 --> 40:35.010
we can catch them in the act.

40:36.840 --> 40:38.300
That's all for today then.

40:38.320 --> 40:39.840
We'll continue the investigation.

40:39.840 --> 40:40.440
Tomorrow,

40:40.510 --> 40:42.440
proceed with your sales as normal.

40:42.590 --> 40:43.840
I'll send plainclothes officers

40:43.840 --> 40:44.900
to patrol the area.

40:45.510 --> 40:45.880
Okay.

40:46.230 --> 40:46.830
Thank you.

40:47.960 --> 40:48.550
Thank you for your trouble.

40:48.550 --> 40:49.150
Thank you.

40:57.590 --> 40:58.790
Let me drive you home.

40:58.920 --> 41:00.450
So you can have a good sleep.

41:00.800 --> 41:01.880
Let's not go back and forth.

41:01.880 --> 41:03.340
I'll just sleep in the car.

41:04.760 --> 41:05.360
All right.

41:21.590 --> 41:23.790
I took every precaution against a fire,

41:24.710 --> 41:27.840
but I never expected the accident
to be someone falling.

41:28.760 --> 41:30.280
My chaotic memories

41:31.110 --> 41:32.770
and useless precognition...

41:33.920 --> 41:34.800
Am I unworthy

41:34.800 --> 41:36.190
of everyone's trust?

41:40.800 --> 41:41.550
Zhou Cheng.

41:42.510 --> 41:44.000
Lately, I've been hearing

41:44.000 --> 41:45.200
the sound of an alarm.

41:46.030 --> 41:47.880
Do you think it's a warning?

41:55.400 --> 41:56.530
Don't overthink it.

41:57.230 --> 41:59.360
What matters most
is dealing with the present.

41:59.360 --> 42:00.760
You've done really well.

42:01.710 --> 42:02.630
We've got all the risk factors

42:02.630 --> 42:03.590
under control.

42:05.840 --> 42:06.770
You're too tired

42:08.000 --> 42:09.000
and too tense.

42:11.510 --> 42:12.480
You need to rest.

42:16.150 --> 42:17.440
I truly

42:18.070 --> 42:18.840
hope Luo Yaozong

42:18.840 --> 42:19.980
can make it through this critical period

42:19.980 --> 42:20.910
and wake up soon.

42:23.190 --> 42:25.390
I hope everything can go well tomorrow,

42:25.840 --> 42:27.300
and I hope all our hard work

42:28.070 --> 42:29.230
won't go to waste.

42:30.800 --> 42:31.530
Don't worry.

42:32.920 --> 42:33.670
It won't.

42:37.360 --> 42:37.960
Sleep now.

42:48.230 --> 42:49.290
Get some good rest.

42:52.000 --> 42:52.510
Okay.

42:59.550 --> 43:00.030
Go to sleep.
